Linus,
Please do:
git pull \
git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/paulus/powerpc.git merge
to get a collection of bug-fixes for powerpc, for the Cell, 4xx and
52xx platforms.
Thanks,
Paul.
